snippet.title: Overwatch Theatrical Teaser | "We Are Overwatch"
snippet.description:
The future is now. Are you with us? To learn more and sign up for the beta, visit http://www.playoverwatch.com

Making its debut in select theaters nationwide, this is the first official Overwatch™ teaser. Team up and accomplish the incredible with a diverse cast of soldiers, scientists, adventurers, and oddities!  

Like Us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/playoverwatch   
Follow Us on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/playoverwatch
